      "title": "Ensuring Pay for Our Military Act of 2011", 
      "type": "short"
    }, 
    {
      "as": "introduced", 
      "title": "A bill to appropriate such funds as may be necessary to ensure that members of the Armed Forces, including reserve components thereof, and supporting civilian and contractor personnel continue to receive pay and allowances for active service performed when a funding gap caused by the failure to enact interim or full-year appropriations for the Armed Forces occurs, which results in the furlough of non-emergency personnel and the curtailment of Government activities and services.", 
